Class ClassCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • coverage.ClassCode

  • public class ClassCode
extends java.lang.Object
    ClassCode represents a class inside the application, containing the package name, class name and a list of methods found in class.
    Author:
    Samuel Santos, Julio Henrique
